{"tid":1330204,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愚樂台會然分享下自己做練習生嗰陣嘅經歷","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T00:10:32.000Z","uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"41e548e786937f7c43325c4026ff244bb50aa5c6","tid":1330204,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"知道愚樂台有唔少會員都係做緊練習生<br />\n甚至乎已經出咗道<br />\n所以特登畀個機會<br />\n你哋分享下自己做練習生嗰陣嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小妹係某一間韓國大型娛樂公司做trainee<br />\n某一日見到一個新嘅練習生加入我哋<br />\n嗰陣佢係肥嘟嘟個高高地咁啦<br />\n佢第一眼見到我 <br />\n就即刻喊咁口跑走咗<br />\n我到今時今日都唔知點解佢會喊<br />\n有冇人可以同我講原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6700b3bd9073923a4bf9bb94255ea0acfbebab4a","tid":1330204,"uid":208486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"太樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b5fdd0c80030f5f259b5cd31022c80ccc8113d","tid":1330204,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3f80bec197d1e6ebc7a3a78681f15de32ffd4a","tid":1330204,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6700b3bd9073923a4bf9bb94255ea0acfbebab4a","tid":1330204,"uid":208486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"太樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n真㗎<br />\n小妹自問個樣都唔差喎🤔"},{"pid":"2e11489533db5487c22ca10367229ed23924e06c","tid":1330204,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f3f80bec197d1e6ebc7a3a78681f15de32f